                            <comment id="113059" author="adilger" created="Tue, 21 Apr 2015 17:53:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is caused by the test in the master client added from &quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5729&quot; title=&quot;VFS: Busy inodes after unmount of loop0. Self-destruct in 5 seconds. Have a nice day...&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5729&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5729&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; osd: iput in case of error in osd_scrub_setup&quot; patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/12325&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/12325&lt;/a&gt; so we need to add an exception to this test to skip it for older servers.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
